pages.title: skill-tree
pages.description: An MVP of an SPA where teachers can create skill trees for students. The application is not complete. In the complete version, teachers would be able to receive feedback from their students about how confident they feel about a topic, among many other features. When it comes to making education more student-centered, I believe a step in the right direction is to make it a more fun game to play through the use of skill trees.
